query:
UPDATE users
SET
    profile_markdown = ?,
    profile_rendered_html = ?,
    preferred_tts_result_visibility = ?,
    preferred_w2l_result_visibility = ?,
    discord_username = ?,
    twitter_username = ?,
    twitch_username = ?,
    github_username = ?,
    cashapp_username = ?,
    website_url = ?,
    ip_address_last_update = ?,
    version = version + 1

WHERE users.token = ?
LIMIT 1
